'''Alan Truscott''' is a [[English|English]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.
Truscott was inducted into the [[American Contract Bridge League]]'s Hall of Fame in 2001.<ref name="ACBL HOF">{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
 | author = 
 | publisher = ACBL
 | url = http://www.acbl.org/about/hall-of-fame/members/truscott-alan
 | date =
 | accessdate = 2016-07-31 }}</ref>

